&lt;li&gt;Cloud data platforms: Azure Data Services (preferred), AWS, or Google Cloud Platform&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Warehousing: Synapse, Snowflake, BigQuery, Redshift, etc.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
